    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of her\u2014she\u2019s in truly pristine condition and drives like a total dream. It\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the lot! Whether you're cruising around town or headed on a road trip, this gem is ready to go. I'm honestly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 46500.0,
