    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a superlative example of the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 powertrain. The naturally aspirated induction remains crisp, delivering linear torque through a precise 6-speed manual transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock. This chassis is structurally pristine, featuring the weight-saving carbon fiber roof and flawless subframe mounting points. Critically, the rod bearings have been proactively replaced with WPC-treated units and the throttle actuators uprated, neutralizing the platform\u2019s primary mechanical vulnerabilities. The suspension geometry is factory-spec with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) functioning perfectly. No fluid seepage, no thermal cycling fatigue on plastics, and a concours-level underside.",
